OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will stay
OL,6,Fcloudy through the evening and
OL,7,Fovernight. Some light rain or drizzle
OL,8,Faffecting much of the region but
OL,9,Fstaying dry towards Inverness and
OL,10,FNairn.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA cloudy start for all with
OL,13,Fpatchy rain or drizzle in the west.
OL,14,FEastern parts brightening up through
OL,15,Fthe afternoon with some warm sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
