OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FStaying largely cloudy with spells of
OL,7,Frain in the west. Staying largely dry
OL,8,Fwith a few bright spells towards
OL,9,FInverness and Nairn. Freshening
OL,10,Fwesterly winds on Thursday
